i’ve been using a lot of time to soak in each moment as it is, when it happens. i’ve focused on the past and held on to things that no longer serve me. grief can come from all kinds of loss but the funniest feeling from grieving is grieving living people who are just no longer in your life. growing apart, one sided relationships, disagreements, change of paths, different mindsets, and there are so many other reasons for this funny feeling. i think it seems inevitable while you have people in your life. they come and they go, you learn from them, sometimes they’re not meant to stay forever and you have to keep carrying on with your journey. what else are you to do but bloom?💐

node.text:
my jeeps packed to camp but i have no plans, just itchy feet to keep going. i know plans never go as expected, so much so, that before i left for my road trip, i stopped mapping places to go along the way because i had a feeling nothing would turn out as expected. when i do plan, i start getting my hopes up for certain stops and i didn’t want to let myself down. so i stopped planning. i just let the wind take me because i knew i’d be alright no matter what happened. now i’m home, but i don’t feel at home. i feel antsy and ready to go. 

cue freebird by lynyrd skynyrd

#camping #itchyfeet #onthego #carcamping #jeepcamping #explore #getoutside #freshair #human

node.text:
ITS MY DADS BIRTHDAY💛🎂 we haven’t had a sleepover since i moved out when i was 18, so this trip was just everything to me even if we didn’t make it to any hikes and our trip didn’t go as planned. i’m so thankful for the time we got to spend together in lil tiny chappell, nebraska. we went to all three restaurants, went bowling, went to the coffee shop, sat outside the courthouse in the grass for hours, walked the whole town, watched trains drive by, i got to make him dinner while he read his book and relaxed. i’m just super thankful for us getting to just hangout like this in general. i wish i could hangout with him today💙 

#roadtrip #dadtime #dad #camping #cooking #goodvibes #adventure #smalltown #nebraska
